  </div>
</div>

<!-- ABOUT -->
<section class="about section-light" id="about">
  <div class="section-label" data-i18n="about_label">About the Project</div>
  <h2 class="section-title" data-i18n="about_title">An <em>Integrated Township</em> Built for Tomorrow</h2>
  <div class="divider"></div>
  <div class="about-grid">
    <div class="about-img-wrap fade-up">
      <img src="C:\Users\vsaha\OneDrive\Desktop\OMAXE\WhatsApp Image 2026-04-13 at 1.20.24 PM.jpeg"
           alt="Omaxe Super Corridor Master Plan"
           style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;"
           onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;base64,'" />
      <div class="about-note">450 Acres<br/><span style="font-size:.78rem;font-weight:400;opacity:.8" data-i18n="about_note">Integrated Township</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="about-content fade-up">
      <p data-i18n="about_p1">Omaxe Super Corridor Indore is a landmark residential plotting project strategically located in Indore's Super Corridor — the city's most dynamic growth zone, home to IT parks, educational institutions, and major business hubs.</p>
      <p data-i18n="about_p2">The township spans 450 acres with a ₹1,200 crore investment, offering a self-sustained ecosystem with residential plots, commercial spaces, retail outlets, educational zones, and healthcare facilities.</p>
      <p data-i18n="about_p3">Whether you're a family seeking a dream home or an investor looking for long-term land appreciation in one of India's fastest-growing Tier-2 cities, Omaxe Super Corridor offers an unmatched opportunity.</p>
      <div class="about-features">
        <div class="about-feature" data-i18n="feat1">Gated community</div>
        <div class="about-feature" data-i18n="feat2">Wide internal roads</div>
        <div class="about-feature" data-i18n="feat3">24×7 security</div>
        <div class="about-feature" data-i18n="feat4">Landscaped greens</div>
        <div class="about-feature" data-i18n="feat5">RERA applied</div>
        <div class="about-feature" data-i18n="feat6">Bank loan facility</div>
        <div class="about-feature" data-i18n="feat7">Commercial &amp; retail</div>
        <div class="about-feature" data-i18n="feat8">Metro connectivity</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

